data.description:
Charm on Five Acres!  Live a Sustainable Farm & Garden Lifestyle in Picturesque Hartford. Spacious Saltbox colonial on private wooded lot with open space and meandering stream. This beautiful home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Additional first floor den/office could be utilized as bedroom and smaller second floor bedroom an office/den. Third floor walk-up has bonus space for game room or hobby space. Walk-out basement has ample space for workshop or could also be finished. Hughes high speed internet-- satellite. 
Showings to begin Sunday10/1/23 with open house 1-3pm.
